Class.name: InterfaceDiskSpace.DataLog
Class.Description: Used to persist data usage for the Ensemble interface testing. See <class>InterfaceDiskSpace.Main</class> for details.

Property.name: BeforeRunData
Property.Description: Data captured before the test run in order to compare later

Property.name: AfterRunData
Property.Description: Data captured after the test run to calculate the sizing used for the test

Property.name: AfterPurgeData
Property.Description: Data captured after purge in order to verify everything was purged
